# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Crit 2048 — Root .gitignore
#
#  Design principle: A fresh `git clone` + `npm install` + `build.bat`
#  should produce ALL deliverables without any extra steps.
#
#  What is committed:
#    ✅ All game source (js/, css/, index.html)
#    ✅ Vendor files (vendor/three.min.js, vendor/html2canvas.min.js)
#    ✅ Vendor fonts (vendor/fonts/*.ttf)
#    ✅ Generated Tailwind CSS (css/tailwind.css) — so browser open works
#    ✅ Tailwind build input + config (css/tailwind-input.css, tailwind.config.js)
#    ✅ Android project (src-tauri/gen/android/) including signing config
#    ✅ Build scripts (scripts/, build.bat)
#    ✅ Tauri config (src-tauri/tauri.conf.json, Capabilities, Cargo.toml)
#
#  What is NOT committed:
#    ❌ node_modules/ — restored by npm install
#    ❌ .web-build/   — generated by npm run prebuild
#    ❌ dist/         — generated by build.bat (deliverables, may be large)
#    ❌ Rust target/  — compiled by cargo (in src-tauri/.gitignore)
#    ❌ Secrets/env   — .env files
#    ❌ Build log     — build_log.txt
#    ❌ OS cruft      — .DS_Store, Thumbs.db
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── npm / Node ────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
.pnp
.pnp.js
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
package-lock.json

# ── Build outputs (generated — do not commit) ─────────────────
.web-build/
dist/

# ── Build artifacts + logs ────────────────────────────────────
build_log.txt
output_terminal_log.txt

# Build backups (local only, can be large binaries)
.build_backups/

# ── Secrets / environment ─────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── OS files ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
ehthumbs.db

# ── IDE / Editor ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Tauri dev artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────
# (Rust target dir is handled by src-tauri/.gitignore)

# ── NOTE: The following are intentionally TRACKED ─────────────
# vendor/three.min.js           — offline Three.js dependency
# vendor/html2canvas.min.js     — offline html2canvas dependency
# vendor/fonts/*.ttf            — offline Cinzel font (no Google Fonts CDN)
# css/tailwind.css              — pre-generated Tailwind output for direct browser use
# css/tailwind-input.css        — Tailwind v4 build input
# tailwind.config.js            — Tailwind config reference
# src-tauri/gen/android/        — Android project + signing
# src-tauri/gen/android/app/keystore.properties — signing config
# src-tauri/gen/android/app/release.jks          — signing keystore
